research.NEWRUNICS.title=New Runics

research.NEWRUNICS.stage.1=I have begun researching the art of imbuing magical properties into wearable baubles. By infusion onto simple baubles, I can create enchanted items that provide their wearer with unique abilities. These runic charms will be a new way to harness the power of the magic in a portable and versatile form.
research.NEWRUNICS.stage.2=The process of crafting runic baubles is more intricate than I first imagined. Each piece requires careful infusion elements. With this knowledge, I can now create baubles that offer powerful protections and enhancements to those who wear them.<PAGE/><BR>§lVerdant Ring§r<BR/>The Verdant Ring is imbued with the power of nature, cleansing its wearer from all negative effects. The ring automatically purifies any harmful potion effects afflicting the wearer; however, it comes with a cooldown of 40 seconds. This ability is invaluable for those who find themselves frequently facing curses or debuffs, offering consistent protection in the face of danger. The ring is quiet, subtle, and a vital defense for those venturing into dangerous realms where malevolent magics lurk.<PAGE/><BR>§lRunic Charge Ring§r<BR/>The Runic Charge Ring holds within it the raw energy of ancient runes. Once worn, the ring grants the bearer both physical might and the resilience of fire immunity. Its runic power increases the wearer's strength, allowing them to deal more damage in combat. Simultaneously, it shields them from fiery environments, making them immune to flames and lava. The combination of strength and fire resistance makes the Runic Charge Ring a powerful tool for adventurers venturing into fiery dungeons or battling fearsome, flame-wielding foes.<PAGE/><BR>§lEnder Ring§r<BR/>The Ender Ring is attuned to the chaotic energies of the End dimension. When the wearer is harmed and their health drops below a critical level, the ring activates its protective magic, teleporting them to a random location, similar to the chorus fruit's unpredictable effect. This emergency teleportation provides a swift escape from dangerous situations. However, it comes with a cooldown of 80 seconds, meaning the wearer must use it wisely and strategically. The Ender Ring offers a lifeline for those who frequently face overwhelming threats but are resourceful enough to rely on its chaotic magic.<PAGE/><BR>§lZombie Heart Amulet§r<BR/>The Zombie Heart Amulet is a unique artifact that houses the soul of a Furious Zombie. Should the wearer fall into dire straits, with their health critically low, the amulet shatters, releasing the enraged zombie to protect its master. The summoned Furious Zombie aggressively attacks nearby enemies, offering a final line of defense when the wearer is most vulnerable. The amulet can also be activated manually, allowing the wearer to call upon the Furious Zombie at will to aid them in combat. However, once broken, the amulet is destroyed, and a new one must be crafted to house another zombie soul.<PAGE/><BR>§lRegeneration Ring§r<BR/>The Regeneration Ring draws upon the very essence of life, granting the wearer periodic surges of healing. Every 13 seconds it radiates a verdant glow, applying Regeneration I for 3 seconds. The effect stacks: each additional ring raises the regeneration level (Regeneration II, III, etc.), ensuring ever‑quicker recovery for those who don more than one.<PAGE/><BR>§lRevive Ring§r<BR/>When a fatal strike would drop its bearer, the Revive Ring intervenes, halting damage at 1 health. All negative effects are instantly cleansed, and the ring then enters a 5‑minute cooldown. This single‑use salvation offers a second chance to anyone caught in truly desperate circumstances.<PAGE/><BR>§lHaste Ring§r<BR/>The Haste Ring is inscribed with ancient magic that lightens the burden of spellcraft. For each ring worn, caster cooldowns are reduced. Effects stack multiplicatively: every extra ring further trims cooldown times, making this relic indispensable for prolonged confrontations.


research.REVIVE_SKELET.title=Revive Skeleton
research.REVIVE_SKELET.stage.1=Revive Skeletons<DIV> are an enigma of magic and decay. Bound together by ancient spells, they roam not as mere undead but as fragments of lost rituals, pulsing with dark energy. Each bone whispers secrets of forbidden arts, a chilling reminder of the power that bends death to its will. I've noticed that some of these skeletons harbor mysterious scrolls within their chests. What secrets might they hold?

research.TIMESTONE.title=The Temporal Catalyst
research.TIMESTONE.stage.1=I have begun unraveling temporal mechanics in earnest. By anchoring a stable focus point, I can accelerate local processes without tearing the field apart. The wider the area and the stronger the acceleration, the more precision this work demands.
research.TIMESTONE.stage.2=§lTime Stone§r<DIV><BR>I found that this stone asks for no coal and no essentia as fuel; it seems to feed on the cadence of the moment itself. Within its sphere (7x7x7, radius 3), it accelerates local time for working mechanisms, forcing them to complete their operations faster than normal.<BR>Important: this effect applies to mechanisms and devices only; living entities are unaffected.<PAGE>Yet the art is temperamental: when two Time Stones share the same field, they smother one another and the acceleration falls silent. If I desire stable operation, I must place them apart.


thaumicforever.enchantment.voidrepair=Void Repair
research.FOCUSCALM.title=Focus Effect: Clouded Mind
research.FOCUSCALM.stage.1=Not every victory demands a strike. By threading the Aspect of Mind through a softened focus pattern, I can briefly mute hostile impulse in lesser creatures.
research.FOCUSCALM.stage.2=With finer concentration, the hush lingers longer. The subject is not made loyal, only quieted, until pain or fresh provocation breaks the veil.

research.CHAINFLIGHT.title=Focus Effect: Chains of Flight
research.CHAINFLIGHT.stage.1=Airborne foes place too much faith in height. By weaving the Aspect of Trap into a weighted arcane chain, I can seize their lift and pull them down.
research.CHAINFLIGHT.stage.2=The reinforced weave holds harder and longer. Wing, levitation, and spell-borne ascent are all suppressed while the chain endures.
research.FOCUSBEAM.title=Focus Medium: Sky Beam
research.FOCUSBEAM.stage.1=I shaped a sustained beam conduit instead of a single projectile release. Once cast, the medium anchors a luminous channel in the aimed direction and keeps the stream stable for several seconds.
research.FOCUSBEAM.stage.2=The beam now propagates linked focus effects in pulses while the channel persists, repeatedly applying the next stage along the traced line. Precision in aim matters: the stream continually updates to the current hit point.

research.NEWAUROMANCY.title=Mastery of the Auromancy
research.NEWAUROMANCY.stage.1=I returned to first principles of focuscraft: pattern geometry, flow discipline, and resonance balance. Only then did I understand how to assemble more complex lenses without collapsing the matrix.
research.NEWAUROMANCY.stage.2=I can now craft new composite lenses by binding multiple effects into a single focus, in the manner of greater focuswork. This is not brute amplification but technical mastery: complex combinations become steadier, more predictable, and less wasteful in vis.
research.NEWAUROMANCY.addenda.1=An empty lens reveals itself not as unfinished glass, but as a stable foundation for deeper focus architecture. With proper layering, I can now craft improved composite foci suited for complex effect combinations.
research.GREAT_ARO.title=Greater Auromancy
research.GREAT_ARO.stage.1=What I mastered before was only a foundation. By refining focus geometry and stabilizing resonance, I can drive much denser vis flow without tearing the casting matrix apart.
research.GREAT_ARO.stage.2=Greater Auromancy is not a different art, but a deeper one. Under heavy load, patterns stay steadier, channel more power, and waste less vis.

research.FOCUSCLEANSE.title=Focus Effect: Cleansing the body
research.FOCUSCLEANSE.stage.1=Order is correction as much as structure. A simple Ordo-biased pattern lets me strip harmful arcane residue from a target on contact.
research.FOCUSCLEANSE.stage.2=With refinement, the cleansing lattice persists briefly and continues removing fresh corruption before it can settle.

research.MINDCONTROL.title=Focus Effect: Dominion over Minds
research.MINDCONTROL.stage.1=A risky Mind-imprint allows me to seize weaker wills and redirect hostile intent toward nearer threats.
research.MINDCONTROL.stage.2=My suppression now reaches deeper, allowing me to intercept hostile will and turn it inward. Why cut down every foe myself, when I can force their ranks to tear each other apart?

research.NEWARTIFICE.title=New Artifice
research.NEWARTIFICE.stage.1=I have moved beyond simple arcane tools and started designing true hybrid mechanisms: devices where magical flow and mechanical logic support each other instead of competing.
research.NEWARTIFICE.stage.2=My newer designs prove that careful engineering can make unstable arcane principles practical. Proper casings, calibrated channels, and staged discharge loops let these machines run consistently in field conditions.<PAGE>§lTime Trap§r<BR>The Time Trap is my first successful tactical prototype in this line. It condenses temporal distortion into a throw-capable frame and releases it on impact, slowing movement in the affected zone.<IMG>thaumicforever:textures/misc/time_trap.png:0:0:255:255:0.5</IMG><BR>Accurate placement matters: a misplaced trap wastes charge, while a precise one can decide a fight before it begins.<PAGE>
research.ADVARTIFICE.title=Advanced Artifice
research.ADVARTIFICE.stage.1=The first machines taught me that brass is sufficient for motion, thaumium for obedience, and void metal for endurance. By comparing their gears under stress, I can begin designing mechanisms that do not merely contain magic, but regulate it with intent.
research.ADVARTIFICE.stage.2=Advanced Artifice is the discipline of making arcane machinery think in small, reliable steps. Layered gear trains, warded housings, and void-sunk tolerances allow a device to hold power longer, discharge it cleaner, and survive mistakes that would tear simpler work apart.
research.FLUXSCRUBBER.title=Flux Scrubber
research.FLUXSCRUBBER.stage.1=I needed a cheap, practical answer to recurring Flux buildup, so I started developing a rough scrubber from common materials. It is not elegant and not precise, but it is affordable and useful for everyday containment.
research.FLUXSCRUBBER.stage.2=§lFlux Scrubber§r<BR>This is a crude tool, not a surgical instrument. Every 20 seconds it emits one pulse in its current aura chunk: with a 50% chance it removes Flux, and with a 50% chance it removes Vis.<BR>In short: inexpensive, practical, and intentionally inaccurate.

research.GUARD.title=Guardian Stand
research.GUARD.stage.1=You've discovered a way to use magic to alive a simple wooden armor stand. Through the infusion of magic, this stand can be transformed into a loyal guardian.
research.GUARD.stage.2=With the proper application of magic dust, your newly awakened sentinel will defend you from threats, ready to serve its master at all times.<PAGE><BR><IMG>thaumicforever:textures/misc/research2.png:0:0:255:255:0.5</IMG>
 
research.NEWINFUSION.title=New Infusion Enchantment
research.NEWINFUSION.stage.1=Through careful study of ancient magical techniques, you have unlocked the ability to perform infusion enchantments. This form of magic allows you to imbue your tools, weapons, and armor with powerful enchantments that exceed those of traditional means. By utilizing magical energy, you can infuse objects with aspects that will enhance their abilities and grant them additional properties.
research.NEWINFUSION.stage.2=I have made progress in understanding advanced infusion enchantments, which allow powerful effects to be embedded directly into equipment. Each additional rank of the same enchantment will cost more essentia and increase the chance of instability. Different infusion enchantments applied together further raise these costs, and may also inflict the item with Warp.<BR>Not all enchantments are universal — each has specific item types they can be applied to, listed below.<BR>Infusion-enchanted tools can still be used with a standard enchanting table, and sneaking suppresses any active effect while in use.<PAGE>§oVoid Repair§r<DIV>This enchantment causes the item to slowly regenerate durability over time, repairing itself without any user action.<DIV>§oRanks§r: 1<BR>§oTarget§r: any<PAGE>§oPoison§r<DIV>Applies a poison effect when striking a target. At higher ranks, the poison becomes withering. May destabilize the surrounding aura.<DIV>§oRanks§r: 1-7<BR>§oTarget§r: weapon<PAGE>§oRuby Protection§r<DIV>Deals damage to attackers when the wearer is hit. This retaliation increases with enchantment rank and manifests visually as a red glyph flash. At total Ruby Protection level 10 or higher, attackers are also set on fire.<DIV>§oRanks§r: 1-15<BR>§oTarget§r: armor<PAGE>§oBleeding§r<DIV>On hit, the target starts bleeding and takes wither-like damage over time. Stronger ranks increase the bleed severity.<DIV>§oRanks§r: 1-5<BR>§oTarget§r: weapon
research.NEWINFUSION.addenda.1=§oUnbreakable§r<DIV>When this seal awakens, steel remembers the first laws of creation. Edges do not dull, plates do not crack, and time itself fails to wear the artifact down.<DIV>§oRanks§r: 1<BR>§oTarget§r: any


