research.THAUMICFOREVER.stage.1=The first steps are always the hardest. The book insists that no wand can be born without proper fittings. I must combine a rod with a pair of caps at an Arcane Workbench to assemble my first wand.<BR>It also hints at another trick: a simple Wood Table can be awakened to greater purpose. Right-click the Wood Table with a wand, and it will transform into a Wand Workbench.
research.THAUMICFOREVER.stage.2=A wand is more than a tool; it is a vessel for Vis. The Wand Workbench draws upon this reserve to shape arcane crafts.<BR>It seems the wand itself can replace a pinch of Salis Mundus when awakening a table. For now I only know that it stores Vis and lends it to the workbench. Of its deeper nature, I know little yet.
research.THAUMICFOREVER.stage.3=By joining two greatwood tables and applying salis mundus, I can obtain a research table. Yet its true nature remains unclear to me.<BR>I will keep this page open, for it seems destined to hold further notes as my studies advance.
research.THAUMICFOREVER.addenda.1=A Revive Skeleton yielded a strange scroll, its text fractured and incomplete. Perhaps I should return to the research table and see if it responds to these hints.<PAGE><IMG>thaumicforever:textures/misc/table1.png:0:0:255:255:0.5</IMG><BR>Understanding the functionality of the DoubleTable is crucial for advancing in thaumic studies. The table is split into several key functional zones:<BR><IMG>thaumicforever:textures/misc/table2.png:0:0:255:255:0.5</IMG><BR>*Green Slot:* Items placed here will have their aspects extracted. This slot handles the extraction process when interacting with the system.<BR>*Red Slot:* This area holds extracted aspects.The system processes these aspects for research or further synthesis.<BR>*Yellow Circle:* The visualization area displays the current aspects stored in the system. Use this area to plan further research efficiently.<PAGE><BR><IMG>thaumicforever:textures/misc/table3.png:0:0:255:255:0.5</IMG>To progress, ensure your table setup is correct, and provide the necessary components to extract aspects.
research.THAUMICFOREVER.addenda.2=The advanced gauntlet has proven a worthy refinement. Replacing iron with brass improved its handling of Vis, and each further upgrade brings the focus closer to the ideal I seek.
research.THAUMICFOREVER.addenda.3=The road is long for a thaumaturge, and gathering supplies soon becomes a burden. To ease this, I have devised a pouch that can carry the essentials of any journey.

research.NEWALKIMIA.stage.1=I have begun charting the foundations of this new branch of alchemy.
research.NEWALKIMIA.stage.2=My command of this alchemical discipline has grown noticeably stronger.

research.PERMUTATIOALKIMIA.stage.1=By attuning salis mundus to Permutatio, I can unify entropy, order and life transmutations into one mutable school.
research.PERMUTATIOALKIMIA.stage.2=Permutatio now governs decomposition and restructuring alike; the merged crucible formulae answer this single doctrine.

research.HERBAALKIMIA.stage.1=I am mapping Herba Alchemy through the living essences of plants and growth.
research.HERBAALKIMIA.stage.2=The inner workings of Herba Alchemy now stand clear before me.
research.SEED.title=Nature Seed
research.SEED.stage.1=After mastering Herba Alchemy, I can move from simple plant transmutation to engineered growth. By stabilizing life-aspects inside a dense seed core, I should create a true super-fertilizer for trees.
research.SEED.stage.2=The Nature Seed is complete. It greatly amplifies tree growth speed and can force oak saplings to develop into the same towering forms found in the Magical Forest.

research.VICTUSALKIMIA.stage.1=I have returned to Victus-aligned alchemy, where vital resonance binds growth, flesh and restorative transmutation into one coherent branch.
research.VICTUSALKIMIA.stage.2=Victus now serves as the stable life junction of my alchemical progression.

research.TERRAALKIMIA.stage.1=I have entered Terra Alchemy through the patient study of earth-aligned materials.
research.TERRAALKIMIA.stage.2=I have mastered Terra's fundamentals and unlocked a new crucible path.

research.AQUAALKIMIA.stage.1=I began Aqua Alchemy by gathering reagents resonant with flowing essence.
research.AQUAALKIMIA.stage.2=Its principles now move naturally through my practice.

research.PRAECANTATIOALKIMIA.stage.1=I have initiated Praecantatio Alchemy, where Vis itself becomes reagent and catalyst.
research.PRAECANTATIOALKIMIA.stage.2=I can now wield Praecantatio methods with stable control.

research.ADDITIONALALKIMIA.stage.1=I have opened supplementary branches of alchemy and begun integrating their theory.
research.ADDITIONALALKIMIA.stage.2=My alchemical framework now includes these extended methods.

research.APPLIDALKIMIA.stage.1=I have started Applied Alchemy, where arcane process meets modern machinery.
research.APPLIDALKIMIA.stage.2=I can now integrate magic and technology into one working system.

research.BOTANIAALKIMIA.stage.1=I have begun Botania Alchemy by fusing natural resonance with arcane method.
research.BOTANIAALKIMIA.stage.2=These floral formulae now answer to my hand.

research.IMMERALKIMIA.stage.1=I have entered Immersive Alchemy, binding furnace craft and arcane transmutation.
research.IMMERALKIMIA.stage.2=Its forge-bound principles are now fully under my control.

research.IUALKIMIA.stage.1=I have begun Industrial Alchemy, applying automation logic to magical process.
research.IUALKIMIA.stage.2=I have unlocked the core principles of industrial-scale alchemy.



research.RESEARCHPRIMAL.title=Ancient Research
research.RESEARCHPRIMAL.stage.1=During your magical studies, you uncovered cryptic mentions of unknown yet incredibly powerful relics. These artifacts, forged in the dawn of magic, harbor a force beyond mortal comprehension. Legends speak of them as sources of unseen power capable of shifting the very balance of the world. Yet, they also warn: those who dare approach such power may rise to unparalleled heights or be utterly consumed by its weight. Are you prepared to take this step into the unknown?



