research.PRIMAL.title=Primal
research.PRIMAL.stage.1=These entries concern artifacts forged from primal force itself. Their potential reaches beyond ordinary thaumaturgy, bending space and time where lesser tools fail. I must proceed carefully, for such power yields only to the worthy.
research.POTION_GUN.title=Potion Sprayer
research.POTION_GUN.stage.1=§bPotion Sprayer§r<BR>I have reworked the standard potion-spraying mechanism into a portable channel fed directly by vis from the tool itself. Instead of a single burst, it can sustain a controlled alchemical stream along my line of sight.<PAGE>The assembly is temperamental: without a stable vis reserve, pressure drops and the mixture collapses into useless mist. Yet once calibrated, it applies combat and utility effects quickly, without relying on thrown flasks.

research.ETERNAL_BLADE.title=Eternal Blade
research.ETERNAL_BLADE.stage.1=§EEternal Blade§r<BR><IMG>thaumicforever:textures/items/eternal_blade.png:0:0:256:256:0.13</IMG><BR> This blade, infused with malevolent magic, burns with hatred toward all that exists and all that does not. Its edge delivers death and destruction, while its wielder bears the weight of eternal wrath, offering no peace even in moments of triumph.

