research.STUFF.title=Stuff
research.STUFF.stage.1=§bStuff§r<BR>Here I have gathered practical artifacts from my sealed PRIMAL notes.<PAGE>§lPrimal Charm§r<BR>A compact warding relic for body and mind.<IMG>thaumicforever:textures/misc/charm_amin.png:0:0:256:256:0.13</IMG><BR><PAGE>§lCleansing Bottle§r<BR>A field-use vial that releases purifying fluid on demand.<IMG>thaumicforever:textures/items/bottle_clean.png:0:0:256:256:0.13</IMG><BR><PAGE>§lVis Infusion Bottle§r<BR>A reserve charge that reinforces local aura flow when used correctly.<IMG>thaumicforever:textures/items/bottle_vis.png:0:0:256:256:0.13</IMG><BR><BR>More entries will be added as additional primal devices are decoded.

