research.TELEPORT.title=Crystal World
research.TELEPORT.stage.1=§bCrystal World§r<BR><IMG>thaumicforever:textures/items/crystalworld.png:0:0:256:256:0.13</IMG><BR>I have uncovered a silent, empty dimension that accepts only one traveler at a time. This isolated crystalline expanse is untouched by outside interference, and time itself feels unnaturally still there.<BR>It is an ideal personal refuge for risky experiments, hidden storage, and recovery between expeditions.<BR>What else lies dormant in that endless quiet, I cannot yet say.

