research.EXPLOSIONCAST.stage.1=Through my study of the interaction between Fire and Entropy, I have discovered that the release of destructive energy does not need to be entirely chaotic. When properly shaped, a focused magical impulse can produce a localized explosion capable of harming foes while leaving the surrounding environment largely untouched.

research.EXPLOSIONCAST.stage.2=Further experimentation revealed that increasing the power of this spell rapidly erodes its stability. At higher intensities, the explosive force begins to interact violently with matter itself, allowing the blast to tear apart blocks in a manner comparable to TNT or even the crystals of the End. Such power must be wielded with great caution.
