thaumicforever.BLINK.name=Blink
thaumicforever.BLINK.text=Teleports the caster to the impact point. If multiple projectiles are spawned from one cast, Blink triggers only once.
thaumicforever.SKYBEAM.name=Beam
thaumicforever.SKYBEAM.text=Projects a straight vis beam that locks onto the first hit target and passes trajectory to the next focus stage.
research.BLINK.title=Focus Effect: Blink
research.BLINK.stage.1=By bending Motion through a short, stable fold, I can shift my body directly to a marked point in space instead of traversing it.
research.BLINK.stage.2=The fold collapses after the first successful jump in a cast, preventing unstable chain relocation when the spell splits into multiple projectiles.
thaumicforever.PRIMAL.name=Chaos
thaumicforever.PRIMAL.text=Each cast stores a random chain of focus medium/effect and fires it on the next cast.
thaumicforever.PRIMAL_ELEMENT.name=Primal Element Chain
thaumicforever.PRIMAL_ELEMENT.text=If Thaumic Augmentation is present, unleashes Water first, then chains Fire, Frost, and Earth.
thaumicforever.TIMEBOMB.name=Time Cooldown
thaumicforever.TIMEBOMB.text=Delays the next focus stage before it is executed.
