research.CAP_MATERIAL_ALL.title=Exotic Wand Materials
research.CAP_MATERIAL_ALL.stage.0=I should survey foreign magical alloys and fabrics. If a material exists in ore dictionary, it can be adapted into wand parts.
research.CAP_MATERIAL_ALL.stage.1=These are the core exotic caps of my main thaumic line.<BR>§lIchorium§r: strongest vis efficiency (65%) and broad crystal support (all six primals +2).<BR>§lMithrillium§r: balanced efficiency (75%), all primals +1.<BR>§lAdaminite§r: better efficiency (70%), all primals +2.<BR>§lMithminite§r: extreme efficiency (60%), all primals +3.<BR>§lThauminite§r: ordered channeling (85%), Ordo crystal discount +1.<BR>§lAlkimium§r: stable crafting flow (95%), Aqua/Terra/Ordo crystal discount +1.<BR>§lBismuth§r: split order-entropy behavior (85%), Ordo/Perditio crystal discount +1.<PAGE>In practice: lower percent means lower vis cost. For universal efficiency
