research.ESSENTIACRYSTALCONVERTER.title=Essentia Crystallization
research.ESSENTIACRYSTALCONVERTER.stage.0=I have nearly mastered the art of drawing liquid essentia out of matter, so reversing that process is the next useful step. Instead of storing essentia only in jars and pipes, I can force it back into a stable crystalline form.
research.ESSENTIACRYSTALCONVERTER.stage.1=§lCrystallizer§r<BR>The Crystallizer no longer needs a quartz seed. If a port feeds it CV from below, it condenses that aspect directly into a vis crystal at a high cost: 200 CV for one crystal, twice the cost of pushing the same CV into essentia storage.<BR>If no CV is supplied, it falls back to nearby surplus primal aura and forms crystals matching the strongest local primal aspect. It is not an aura totem: it consumes local pressure instead of moving it between chunks.

