research.SEALUSE.addenda.thaumicforever.advanced_use=Further golemancy work has revealed a more flexible version of the Use seal. With better logic patterns, the golem can repeat use tasks and avoid wasting actions on occupied targets.

research.SEALTRADE.title=Control Seal: Trade
research.SEALTRADE.stage.1=Merchant interaction requires more than a simple use command. A golem must identify valid traders, request only trades it can pay for, and ignore exchanges forbidden by its filter.
research.SEALTRADE.stage.2=This control seal lets a golem perform trades using items supplied by nearby provider seals. It can filter wanted or unwanted results and continue past blocked trades instead of stopping at the first failed offer.

research.SEALARCANECASTER.title=Control Seal: Arcane Caster
research.SEALARCANECASTER.stage.1=A golem can follow hostile targets, but ranged thaumaturgy needs more precise behavior. The construct must keep distance, choose valid targets, and channel a caster tool without a thaumaturge's hands.
research.SEALARCANECASTER.stage.2=This control seal lets a golem use caster gauntlets and wands. Its filters can limit casting to enemies, friends, animals, or players depending on the task.

