research.GOLEMSCORE.title=Golem Cores
research.GOLEMSCORE.stage.1=Seals command a golem, but they do not change what the construct fundamentally is. A morphic resonator can reshape that deeper pattern into a removable core: a single specialization installed directly into the golem body.
research.GOLEMSCORE.stage.2=Each golem can hold only one core at a time. Goliath makes the construct larger and tougher, Iron Skin reinforces its body against damage, Swift improves movement speed, and Arcane opens the way for arcane seals and caster automation.

